<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id7851bc42-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s583j–8"><num value="583j–8">§ 583j–8.</num><heading> Authorization of appropriations</heading><subsection style="-uslm-lc:I19" class="indent2 firstIndent-2" id="id7851bc43-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s583j–8/a"><num value="a" class="bold">(a)</num><heading class="bold"> Startup funds</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">For the purposes of <ref href="/us/usc/t16/s583j–3">section 583j–3 of this title</ref>, there are authorized to be appropriated $1,000,000.</p>
</content>
</subsection>
<subsection style="-uslm-lc:I19" class="indent2 firstIndent-2" id="id7851bc44-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s583j–8/b"><num value="b" class="bold">(b)</num><heading class="bold"> Matching funds</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">For the purposes of <ref href="/us/usc/t16/s583j–3">section 583j–3 of this title</ref>, there are authorized to be appropriated $3,000,000 for each of fiscal years 2016 through 2023 to the Secretary of Agriculture to be made available to the Foundation to match, on a one-for-one basis, private contributions made to the Foundation.</p>
</content>
</subsection>
<sourceCredit id="id7851bc45-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/pl/101/593/tIV/s410">Pub. L. 101–593, title IV, § 410</ref>, <date date="1990-11-16">Nov. 16, 1990</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/104/2973">104 Stat. 2973</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/103/106/s3/b">Pub. L. 103–106, § 3(b)</ref>, <date date="1993-10-12">Oct. 12, 1993</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/107/1032">107 Stat. 1032</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/114/54/tII/s201/b">Pub. L. 114–54, title II, § 201(b)</ref>, <date date="2015-09-30">Sept. 30, 2015</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/129/515">129 Stat. 515</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/115/334/tVIII/s8503/b">Pub. L. 115–334, title VIII, § 8503(b)</ref>, <date date="2018-12-20">Dec. 20, 2018</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/132/4847">132 Stat. 4847</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="id7851bc46-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="id7851bc47-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
