<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">2015—Subsec. (b). <ref href="/us/pl/114/54">Pub. L. 114–54</ref> substituted “there are authorized to be appropriated $3,000,000 for each of fiscal years 2016 through 2018” for “during the five-year period beginning <date date="1992-10-01">October 1, 1992</date>, there are authorized to be appropriated $1,000,000 annually”.</p>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">1993—Subsec. (b). <ref href="/us/pl/103/106">Pub. L. 103–106</ref> substituted “beginning <date date="1992-10-01">October 1, 1992</date>” for “following <date date="1990-11-16">November 16, 1990</date>”.</p>
